{"id":232738806,"title":"大家都怎麼打消自殺的念頭","content":"其他學院我是不清楚\n\n但理工學院總有那麼一刻 徬徨無助到讓人想要一了百了\n\n每次一有自殺的念頭時 其實我都很害怕\n\n很害怕身體在腦袋好好想清楚之前就做出了無法挽回的事情\n\n希望大家分享一下都怎麼打消這個念頭的\n\n我是因為\n\n在成大+研究所也五年了 每年都有人想不開\n\n也不是官腔的說自殺對事情沒有幫助(都尋死誰管你那麼多)\n\n但一想到即使轟動一時 還是會以驚人的速度被人們遺忘 覺得就算這麼做還是什麼都沒改變 還得忍受恐懼和痛楚 那又何必呢 不如開心的活著吧\n\n然後現在真的是發現承認自己就是爛反而活的很開心(看到這張meme時，沒笑反而蠻有感觸的)\nhttps://i.imgur.com/QnpZPeq.jpg\n\n\n分享一下吧","excerpt":"其他學院我是不清楚，但理工學院總有那麼一刻 徬徨無助到讓人想要一了百了，每次一有自殺的念頭時 其實我都很害怕，很害怕身體在腦袋好好想清楚之前就做出了無法挽回的事情，希望大家分享一下都怎麼打消這個念頭的","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"abc4fa45-a456-49c6-8948-8981ad0b0f97","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-12-22T13:16:20.930Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-22T13:17:13.039Z","commentCount":55,"likeCount":125,"tags":[],"topics":["自殺","成大"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"成功大學","forumAlias":"ncku","school":"國立成功大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":true,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":118},{"id":"514c2569-fd53-4d9d-a415-bf0f88e7329f","count":5},{"id":"011ead16-9b83-4729-9fde-c588920c6c2d","count":2}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/QnpZPeq.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"225b71b7-1c38-4fea-80b6-af6047521379","url":"https://i.imgur.com/QnpZPeql.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/QnpZPeql.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/QnpZPeql.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-22T13:17:13.039Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-22T13:17:13.039Z"},{"id":"225b71b7-1c38-4fea-80b6-af6047521379","url":"https://i.imgur.com/QnpZPeq.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/QnpZPeq","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/QnpZPeql.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-22T13:17:13.039Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-22T13:17:13.039Z"